      "widgets_values": [
        "A heartwarming cinematic scene unfolds in a sun-drenched suburban garden at golden hour, where a young girl with curly chestnut hair and a denim jacket sprints energetically across the lush green lawn toward her mother, who stands gracefully waiting near a rustic wooden bench. The mother has long flowing brown hair tied back with a floral headband and wears a soft pastel yellow dress that flutters gently in the warm breeze as she extends her arms open to embrace the rushing child. Spatially, the child is positioned in the lower-left foreground moving diagonally upward-right toward the center frame where the mother anchors the composition, ensuring their relative scale remains consistent throughout the sequence without any subject swapping or position reversal. The child's movement is fluid and physically believable, starting with quick footfalls kicking up tiny particles of soil and dry grass, transitioning smoothly into a joyful leap as she closes the distance, while the mother's arms rise naturally from her sides to meet the hug without conflicting simultaneous actions. The camera employs a steady medium-long shot that slowly pushes forward to follow the child's approach, maintaining a slight low angle to emphasize the emotional connection and warmth of the moment, with gentle handheld micro-shakes adding organic realism to the framing. Atmospheric details include dappled sunlight filtering through mature oak trees"
